---
title: Japanese Style Sticky Miso Beef with Mushrooms, Pickled Cucumber and Jasmine Rice
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Japanese Style Sticky Miso Beef in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R44_W25_UK_QR13761-3_Main__7low-e48a3b4d.jpg
